# Secrets — must never enter the image
**/.env
**/*.env
**/e-mail.txt
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/id_rsa*
**/credentials*
**/secrets*

# VCS / CI
.git
.github
.gitignore

# Docs / evidence / infra (not needed at runtime)
docs
infra
charts
scripts
README.md
**/*.md

# Local data / logs / caches
**/logs
**/__pycache__
**/data
**/outputs
**/*.log
